mr croatti unifirst chairman president and ceo joined the company in  under the tutelage of his father and company founder aldo croatti throughout the years he gained valuable firsthand experience by working in virtually all areas of the company excelling in service sales operations and management before being named a senior executive since mr croatti became the companys chief executive officer in  president in  and chairman of the board in  unifirst has more than quadrupled its annual revenues to well over  billion   cynthia croatti executive vice president ms croatti joined the company in 8 as the assistant treasurer and has served as treasurer since 8 she became a director in  and was named the companys executive vice president in  additionally ms croatti has primary responsibility for overseeing the human resources and purchasing functions of unifirst corporation   steven s sintros senior vice president and cfo mr sintros is the senior vice president and chief financial officer of unifirst corporation he has been with the company since  serving as unifirsts finance manager and corporate controller before being promoted to his current position in  his primary responsibility is overseeing all financial functions of the company as well as its information systems department prior to joining unifirst mr sintros worked as an audit manager at ernst and young and at arthur andersen before that   david a difillippo senior vice president operations mr difillippo became senior vice president of operations for unifirst corporation in  he joined the company in  starting out as a service manager was promoted to general manager in 8 and to regional vice president for the central region in  mr difillippo oversees specified laundry regions in the us and canada as well as product management   michael a croatti senior vice president operations mr croatti became senior vice president of service and operations for unifirst corporation in  he joined the company in 8 and was mentored by his father unifirst chairman president and ceo ronald croatti he held many positions in production service and sales before being promoted to branch manager in  general manager in 8 and regional vice president in  mr croatti oversees specified laundry regions in the us as well as the companys overall service operations   bill m ross senior vice president operations mr ross became senior vice president of operations for unifirst corporation in  he joined the company in  and held several sales and operations management positions before being promoted to regional vice president in  mr ross oversees specified laundry regions in the east midwest and southeast us   david m katz senior vice president sales and marketing mr katz joined unifirst corporation as vice president sales and marketing in  prior to joining unifirst mr katz worked for dhl express where he served as the northeast vice president of field sales the northeast vice president of national account sales and senior vice president and general manager of the northeast region   request more information how can we help you  required submit local commitment with coasttocoast coverage founded in 3 publicly traded on the new york stock exchange symbol unf over  billion in annual revenues  facilities in the us canada and europe nearly  million unifirst uniform and work apparel wearers  companyowned manufacturing plants  stateoftheart distribution centers  business customer locations 3 employee team partners learn more about unifirst     forbidden access is denied server error   forbidden access is denied you do not have permission to view this directory or page using the credentials that you supplied cynthia croatti  executive vice president treasurer at unifirst corp news home advertising board and executive moves energy health care hedge funds m  a private equity technology you have    free profiles   left this month    start your free trial ➤ hey we noticed youre a relsci pro subscriber would you like to view t